            "",
            "",
            "<b>And Moshe and Aharon went.</b> Moshe and Aharon went into the Tent of Meeting and prayed for the Nation of Israel, whereupon they went outside and blessed the people, saying, “may the word of Hashem accept your offerings with desire”."
        ],
        [
