            "",
            "",
            "",
            "",
            "",
            "<b>And it was good.</b> He made an announcement in the camp saying, “I was the one who forgot the halachah and Aharon reminded me of it”."
        ],
        [],
        [],
        [],
        [],
        [],
        [],
