            "",
            "",
            "",
            "<b>And you shall fear My Sanctuary.</b> And you shall go to My Sanctuary in fear.",
            "",
            "<b>In the presence of the elderly.</b> In the presence of elders who think in Torah you shall rise and you shall respect a wise man."
        ],
        [
            "",
            "",
            "",
            "",
            "",
            "",
            "",
            "",
            "<b>That curses.</b> Using the Ineffable Name."
        ],
        [],
