            "<b>I will not despise them</b> — in the Babylonian kingdom; My word will not repulse them — in the Median kingdom; to annihilate them — in the Greek kingdom; to break My covenant with them — in the kingdom of Edom; I am Adonoy your God — in the days of Gog."
